{"tid":2225851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南丫海難8周年︱便衣警嘲祭品垃圾 譏市民做戲悼亡魂 陰濕伸腳撠記者","createTime":"2020-10-01T15:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T16:46:46.000Z","uid":226955,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a418bf167c22435305777c3a676b18049bafca9f","tid":2225851,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"南丫海難8周年，「女長毛」雷玉蓮今年繼續於中環4號碼頭旁悼念死難者。悼念集會今年首次受警方阻撓；有便衣警聲稱拜祭用的紙錢是垃圾，又稱雷「做戲」、「消費意外」，並在儀式完成後，向尊重死者而除罩拜祭的雷發告票，稱她違反「口罩令」。其間雷一度情緒激動，反斥警員「冇人性」，「係咪立咗國安法，連南丫海難都唔准拜？」，表明來年會繼續拜祭，希望港人出席悼念。該名便衣警又刻意伸腳，企圖絆倒在場採訪的網媒女記者。幸女記者反應快速，及時跳過「警腿」才未有被絆倒。<br />\n<br />\n雷玉蓮於中環4號碼頭旁設置祭壇，寫有「海難八周年」、「沉痛哀悼39名海難死者」等，備有鮮花、水果、香燭、39份月餅。集會有約10名市民參與，晚上8時24分，即當年海難發生時間，出席市民一同為海難死者默哀8分鐘，象徵海難8周年。之後市民逐一為死難者上香，雷玉蓮亦焚燒冥鏹及向海撒紙錢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M4oiCdh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM4oiCdh.jpg&h=626e380a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n便衣警嘲紙錢垃圾 雷玉蓮收告票仍心甘命抵<br />\n<br />\n集會期間一度有多名防暴警員到場，其中一名便衣警甫到場即稱紙錢為垃圾，要求雷玉蓮終止悼念及拾回散落周圍的紙錢。雷玉蓮感不滿與警員理論，強調紙錢不是垃圾，警員則一度拉起封鎖線，並聲稱會票控雷。雷回應指不介意收告票，「如果你為咗海難告我，我心甘命抵」，要求完成拜祭。<br />\n<br />\n之後該名便衣警又稱海難是「好傷心嘅意外」，斥雷「消費呢場意外」、「做戲」。雷隨即情緒激動，反問該名便衣警「有冇人性」，表明8年來自掏腰包、不籌分毫舉辦悼念集會，一度落淚。亦有出席集會的市民看不過眼，上前與警員理論。<br />\n<br />\n擾攘一番後，警員撤去封鎖線，退至約10米外，有警員一直以攝錄機拍攝。雷玉蓮則逐漸收拾心情繼續拜祭，亦有市民協助拾回周圍紙錢。雷一度步履不穩、近乎暈倒，要由旁人攙扶，但稍作休息後堅持燒完最後一份祭品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t6z51E2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft6z51E2.jpg&h=427dcff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為表尊重除罩拜祭 料被票控早備2,000元<br />\n<br />\n拜祭完成後，警方隨即向雷玉蓮發出告票，該名便衣警稱雷未有戴上口罩，須罰款2,000元。雷稱，自己是佛教徒，平時外出會戴口罩，但拜祭時為表尊重須除下口罩，今日已帶備2,000元，準備隨時受到票控。她稱警員無理阻撓拜祭，怒斥警方「冇人性」，「係咪立咗國安法，連南丫海難都唔准拜？」她指，未來會堅持每年到場拜祭海難，希望來年有更多人出席悼念集會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NtiuJTu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtiuJTu.jpg&h=ddc9b074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n便衣警疑伸腳圖絆倒記者不果 自知理虧無言<br />\n<br />\n警方阻撓雷玉蓮拜祭南丫海難期間，有剛於碼頭落船的市民疑不滿警方做法，高聲批評警員，在場警員隨即發難，截查該名市民。現場記者上前追訪時，該名聲稱拜祭紙錢是垃圾的便衣警，疑伸腳企圖絆倒一名網媒女記者。《蘋果》記者所見，該名便衣警伸出一隻腳幾乎成「一字馬」姿勢，幸女記者反應快速，及時跳過才未有被絆倒。<br />\n<br />\n事後女記者即轉身喝斥該名便衣警，便衣警則疑心虛、自知理虧，不但未有反駁或聲稱女記者襲警，反而着女記者「去啦、影啦」，一反以往警方與傳媒有碰撞時的常態。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kuqte0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuqte0d.jpg&h=40aefa1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伸腳企圖絆倒女記者嘅便衣警"},{"pid":"fc5cd47036dc89f2924126fa6e9c0bc183a6c1b8","tid":2225851,"uid":346701,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"狗嘴特別臭"},{"pid":"29296f518196f39becdaa6f2982579ad1ba720f5","tid":2225851,"uid":269481,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"原來條撚樣唔止講閪話，仲要特登kick人，屌你老母死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f695b47d818fc4c01e563988956b7482b89607ec","tid":2225851,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ea15a020e252a9b8fb3a9d5cff24b3fdcacbf6","tid":2225851,"uid":301666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:38:51.000Z","msg":"法庭（如果上到法庭嘅話）：<br />\n<br />\n記者挑釁在場嘅警員，所以警察先至自衛伸腳，情有可源，獲判無罪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e1e685965de4b9e43195090bf84cf8c4685d71","tid":2225851,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:39:28.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"fdb7369cb86ffdcd0d0913ac32176c4a96420796","tid":2225851,"uid":322732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"呢班冇人性地府都唔收佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d4b3c26bd968554d38178a4bddb872eea5a605","tid":2225851,"uid":38572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"Post 番link 喇<br />\n<br />\n南丫海難8周年︱便衣警嘲祭品垃圾 譏市民做戲悼亡魂 陰濕伸腳撠記者<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/KSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FKSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w120Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=5ec6e130\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FKSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY%2F&h=e1933378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/KSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY/</a>"},{"pid":"8140411eb0739f7b2d98b90dc00de08517d7f05f","tid":2225851,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74ea15a020e252a9b8fb3a9d5cff24b3fdcacbf6","tid":2225851,"uid":301666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:38:51.000Z","msg":"法庭（如果上到法庭嘅話）：<br />\n<br />\n記者挑釁在場嘅警員，所以警察先至自衛伸腳，情有可源，獲判無罪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:43:10.000Z","msg":"去年12月網民發起「和你Shop」行動，大批警員進駐各大商場戒備。有公務員被指在尖沙嘴海洋中心伸腳欲絆倒一名急步行走的便衣警，被控襲警罪。裁判官鄭念慈早前裁定不認罪的被告罪成，並明言會判監。鄭官今判刑時表明，被告伸腳絆倒警員屬偷襲行為，嚴重程度不亞於明目張膽地襲警，惟天網恢恢，有閉路電視拍下被告犯案過程。鄭官強調，法庭絕不姑息此等行為，須判處阻嚇刑罰，終判監2個月。而被告已因本案失去工作。<br />\n<br />\n辯方表示被告會就定罪上訴，向法庭申請保釋。鄭官一度指「一萬元（保釋金）遠遠唔夠」，最終批准被告以現金5萬元保釋，惟須交出旅遊證件、每星期向警署報到4次，每晚10時至翌晨7時宵禁。<br />\n<br />\n鄭官判刑時指，被告用難以察覺的身體動作將警員絆倒，屬偷襲行為，其嚴重程度不亞於明目張膽地襲警。鄭官強調，雖然被告伸腳的動作難以察覺，但天網恢恢，閉路電視攝錄了被告的犯案過程。雖然被絆倒的警員傷勢不算嚴重，但始終有實際受傷，須請三天病假。<br />\n<br />\n鄭官又引述案例指，法庭認為襲擊正在執行職務的警員屬嚴重罪行，重申法庭絕不姑息此等行為，否則前線警員將得不到保障，社會安寧受損，警察士氣大受打擊。縱使被告初犯、品格良好，以及只是一時衝動犯案，仍須負上刑責，量刑起點定於監禁2個月。鄭官認為，被告因本案失去工作完全是咎由自取，並非減刑因素，加上是經審訊後定罪，沒有任何刑期扣減。"},{"pid":"5c31c601b829106846d49283f98d0f8da23b24a5","tid":2225851,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:43:35.000Z","msg":"對待周梓樂祭壇嘅處理方式放落南丫海難度，因為政府覺得南丫海難死難者家屬成日煩住佢"},{"pid":"9783b3fe38feeb4d0b63e5674fc0b98dc02387fc","tid":2225851,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64d4b3c26bd968554d38178a4bddb872eea5a605","tid":2225851,"uid":38572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"Post 番link 喇<br />\n<br />\n南丫海難8周年︱便衣警嘲祭品垃圾 譏市民做戲悼亡魂 陰濕伸腳撠記者<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/KSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FKSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w120Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=5ec6e130\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FKSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY%2F&h=e1933378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/KSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"Thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c32c9b4ec66636202109f28f5abd343a201163","tid":2225851,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d57ac0413543a8c32b7f5d71b0de7a39cfcc531","tid":2225851,"uid":283239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:46:21.000Z","msg":"下次7月7咪大鑼大鼓賀佢老母囉"},{"pid":"1ee99cace4183032962f096b582004fa16ddf62e","tid":2225851,"uid":